textBody:
Elara may refer to one of the following:

*Elara (moon), a moon of Jupiter
*Elara (mythology), the mother of Tityos in Greek mythology
*Elara (timeshare), a Hilton Grand Vacations resort in Las Vegas, Nevada
*Ellalan (monarch), an ancient Sri Lankan king also known as Ellara
*"Elara", a song by Celldweller from Soundtrack for the Voices in My Head Vol. 2
